Josephine Mitchell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Josephine_Mitchell 0 Josephine Mitchell (born 21 May 1965) sometimes billed credited as Jo Mitchell is an Australian actress, comedian and screen writer with a lengthy career in theatre and television soap operas and serials. Mitchell is best known for her role in the television series A Country Practice as schoolgirl Jo Loveday (later Langley), from 1985 until leaving the show in 1989.
